<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
	<title>Background Example1(single image)</title>
	<style>
		body
		{
			background-image: url("https://www.w3schools.com/cssref/img_tree.gif");
			background-repeat: no-repeat;
			background-attachment: fixed;
			background-position: top center;
			background-color: lightblue;
		}

		/*We can write the above code in single line also.
		body
		{
			background: lightblue url("https://www.w3schools.com/cssref/img_tree.gif") no-repeat fixed center;
		}*/
	</style>
</head>
<body>
	<h1>Background Example(single image)</h1>
	<h3>We can write the above code in single line also.</h3>
</body>
</html>
